correctness.rationale: Several schema violations and factual/alignment errors are present despite some correct elements (SALD method, precursors, coinjection, 200 °C, nucleation ~200 cycles, 120 ms exposure, device mobility ~3.5 cm2/V·s). Key issues: (1) Schema/type/unit violations: multiple numeric fields are null (pressure.quantityValue.numericValue, purgeTime.*.quantityValue.numericValue, flowRates.*.quantityValue.numericValue, uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, roughness.value, filmDensity.value), which violates the schema and the “no null” requirement; growthPerCycle unit must be ANGSTROM but was given as NanoM (0.18 nm should be 1.8 Å). (2) Incorrect reactor info: manufacturer set to “ION-TOF GmbH,” which is the LEIS instrument vendor/author affiliation, not the ALD reactor manufacturer mentioned in the paper; reactor details are not provided in the article and should not be fabricated. (3) Film thickness mismatch: 250 nm thickness and 1400 cycles correspond to ZnO-only growth, not the IGZO process; the IGZO TFT film in the article is 15 nm. (4) SupercycleDesign is inappropriate: the article uses co-injection SALD, not supercycles; provided subcycle counts are null and the sequence (In2O3, Ga2O3, ZnO) is not described in the paper. (5) Device vs material property conflation: materialProperties.electricalProperties.mobility (3.5 cm2/V·s) is device FE mobility, not an intrinsic film mobility measurement; should not be duplicated there without supporting Hall data. (6) Missing/unsupported composition data: elemental concentrations left as null despite reported IGZO device composition (In 20%, Ga 8% of total cations); atomicRatio set to “Not Found.” (7) Threshold voltage set to −25 V is weakly supported (the text reports an onset at −25 V and separate Vth trends; explicit Vth for that device is not clearly provided). (8) Purge times provided as null despite SALD not using time-consuming purges; if included, they should be zero rather than null. Properties to correct: replace null numeric fields with valid numbers or omit optional sections; fix GPC unit to Å; correct film thickness and cycles for the IGZO process (15 nm for TFT case), remove/disable SupercycleDesign for co-injection SALD, remove or correct reactor manufacturer, move device mobility only to deviceProperties, add composition values (e.g., In 20%, Ga 8%) with EDX as method, and verify threshold voltage value from the article or leave unspecified if not reported.

completeness.rationale: Extraction is largely incomplete and contains multiple schema violations and factual inconsistencies. Key issues: (1) Many required numeric fields are null, violating the schema: processParameters.pressure.numericValue, thicknessControl.purgeTime[*].precursor/coReactant.numericValue, thicknessControl.flowRates[*].precursorFlow/coReactantFlow/purgingGasFlow.numericValue, materialProperties.uniformity.variation.numericValue, conformality.aspectRatio.numericValue, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values.quantityValue.numericValue, deviceProperties.onOffRatio.numericValue and subthresholdSwing.numericValue. plasmaPower is set to null instead of being omitted. (2) Unit errors: growthPerCycle uses NanoM; schema requires ANGSTROM (0.18 nm should be 1.8 Å). (3) Incoherent mixing of processes: numberofCycles=1400 and filmThickness=250 nm correspond to ZnO (Fig. 1a), not the IGZO process under evaluation; supercycleDesign is filled despite the article using coinjection S-ALD (not a supercycle) and contains null counts. (4) Reactor metadata incorrect: manufacturer listed as ION-TOF GmbH (LEIS instrument vendor), not the S-ALD reactor; omit or correct. (5) Film composition not captured though available: IGZO device example has In=20% and Ga=8% (Fig. 4a); XRD sample has (In+Ga)/(In+Ga+Zn)=28% (Fig. 3d). atomicRatio/value set to 'Not Found' and elementalConcentration left null. (6) Device metrics: thresholdVoltage set to -25 V, which the text describes as onset voltage, not Vth; Fig. 4b reports Vth ranging to ~1 V with Ga; use an appropriate Vth or clearly distinguish onset. (7) Multiple processes described in the article (ZnO, InZnO, IGZO) are not represented as separate process objects; the single process mixes ZnO and IGZO data, reducing semantic coherence. (8) Several speculative or unsupported entries: otherAspects.reproducibility=True lacks support; saturation=True is not substantiated for IGZO. Properties to add or correct: fill valid pressure (atmospheric, e.g., 760 Torr ≈ 760 mmHg), correct GPC units, remove/zero purge times for SALD, remove unsupported flowRates or provide measured values (or restructure per schema expectations), remove supercycleDesign or mark as not applicable, correct reactor info, populate filmComposition with reported In and Ga at.% and corresponding Zn balance, set device Vth from Fig. 4b (or omit if not explicitly given), remove null-valued optional fields, and extract separate processes for ZnO and InZnO or ensure IGZO process does not include ZnO-only data.
